-- German Minister Roettgen Calls for Euro 2012 Boycott, Bild Says
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-04-29T15:11:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/german-minister-roettgen-calls-for-euro-2012-boycott-bild-says.html
German Environment Minister Norbert
Roettgen said politicians should cancel trips to the European
soccer championship in Ukraine, following reports of
mistreatment and abuse against jailed opposition leader  Yulia
Tymoshenko ,  Bild Zeitung  reported, citing an interview.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sara Marley at   smarley1@bloomberg.net  